&lt;p&gt;Diagnostic Cardio-Respiratory Department&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Highly Specialised Cardiac Physiologist – Cardiac Rhythm Management and PCI/Angiography&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Agenda for Change Band 7 &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to the development in the Cardiac Rhythm Management (CRM) service at Calderdale and Huddersfield NHS Foundation Trust we have a vacancy for an enthusiastic, self-motivated individual with an interest in cardiac devices and PCI/Angiography to work in the Invasive team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Calderdale and Huddersfield Foundation Trust has 2 district hospitals, Calderdale Royal Hospital and Huddersfield Royal Infirmary with 10 substantive cardiologists and a state of the art technical cardiology service situated in Halifax West Yorkshire. The Cardio-Respiratory department offers a full range of invasive and non-invasive cardiac techniques, including routine ECGs, 24hr ambulatory monitoring, physiologist led stress testing, echocardiography, stress echo, TOE, diagnostic angiography, PCI, cardiac device implantation including ICD and CRT, physiologist led ILR implantation, pacing and ICD/CRT face-face and remote follow up , Cardiac MRI, CT Angiography and Myocardial Perfusion Scanning. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are seeking a forward thinking applicant who can contribute to the invasive service and lead an area of CRM. This is a full-time post which will be based at Calderdale Royal Hospital and staff are expected to work cross-site at Huddersfield Royal Infirmary as required. You will contribute to the invasive on-call rota.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interested applicants should possess the appropriate Cardiac Physiology qualifications and experience to include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BSc in Clinical Physiology (or equivalent)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intermediate Life Support (ILS)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Registration to RCCP and/or AHCS,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BHRS/HRUK Accreditation (Devices).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive experience at a specialist level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are committed to professional development and you will be encouraged to attain further academic and professional qualifications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
